talked to, which makes sense,

43:03.915 --> 43:08.552
but man, fuck me, it was
all just so jarring.

43:08.553 --> 43:11.422
All that clapping.

43:11.423 --> 43:14.425
I hope it wasn't worthless.

43:14.426 --> 43:19.263
See, they're setting up for a party

43:19.264 --> 43:21.765
