47:58.842 --> 48:00.609
Fuck.

48:03.213 --> 48:05.448
What is all this shit?

48:08.585 --> 48:09.586
Let's get out of here.

48:09.587 --> 48:12.489
Sam, hold on.
Safe's open.

48:12.490 --> 48:15.225
Oh, dude, you've got
