48:15.226 --> 48:16.493
Leave it, man.

48:16.494 --> 48:17.728
Holy shit.

48:17.729 --> 48:18.729
It's all their passports.

48:18.730 --> 48:20.197
Dude, I don't give a shit.
Let's go.

48:20.198 --> 48:21.732
I got to get some shots of you
looking through this shit.

48:21.733 --> 48:23.500
Somebody's coming, Jake, come on.

48:23.501 --> 48:25.601
Come on.

48:27.738 --> 48:29.006
Can I help you guys?

48:29.007 --> 48:31.006
Yeah, we were just looking
for your brother.

48:33.844 --> 48:36.879
His room's just right
around the corner.

48:50.394 --> 48:52.462
Oh, he is not here right now.

48:52.463 --> 48:53.463
Huh?

48:53.464 --> 48:56.033
I completely forgot.
He is busy.

48:56.034 --> 48:57.534
Busy doing what?

48:57.535 --> 49:00.637
I've been telling Allison
and Sarah about him

49:00.638 --> 49:04.141
And they're just so happy
that he's finally here.

49:04.142 --> 49:07.110
So they took him.

49:07.111 --> 49:09.379
Threesomes aren't
particularly Christian,

49:09.380 --> 49:12.149
if I'm remembering
Sunday school correctly.

49:12.150 --> 49:14.151
Well, we all have to sin
every once in a while

49:14.152 --> 49:15.986
as long as Father approves.

49:15.987 --> 49:18.255
He approved getting
your brother laid?

49:18.256 --> 49:20.924
One must not question
what's best for the Parish.

49:20.925 --> 49:22.793
How so?

49:22.794 --> 49:26.396
I love my brother and
I miss him so much.

49:26.397 --> 49:29.066
And I think that he
would be so happy here

49:29.067 --> 49:31.568
and we're just trying
to show him that.

49:31.569 --> 49:35.005
Don't you think he'd
miss New York, his job?

49:35.006 --> 49:36.807
He can be a photographer here.

49:36.808 --> 49:39.810
And he has all these ideas...
This idea about this book

49:39.811 --> 49:41.812
about the Parish, I
think it's brilliant.

49:41.813 --> 49:43.580
And my parents can support him

49:43.581 --> 49:45.916
and we're expanding all
this and we need money.

49:45.917 --> 49:48.685
And if Patrick stays then
we can get the money and...

49:48.686 --> 49:51.088
Yeah, you want your parents
to send money to help

49:51.089 --> 49:52.422
build this place out.

49:52.423 --> 49:55.158
It's a donation.
It's the same as you.

49:55.159 --> 49:58.095
It's... We just need to get
through this next phase

49:58.096 --> 49:59.930
and then we'll be completely fine.

49:59.931 --> 50:01.331
Oh, are you all right?

50:01.332 --> 50:03.533
Yeah. Yeah.

50:03.534 --> 50:06.470
Caroline, I need your assistance.

50:06.471 --> 50:09.071
I'm coming, Father.

50:11.608 --> 50:14.611
If you see Patrick, tell
him to come see us.

50:14.612 --> 50:15.679
Okay.

50:15.680 --> 50:19.216
Just relax.
You're in paradise.

50:19.217 --> 50:21.685
You fellows seem lost.

50:21.686 --> 50:24.354
Do you need someone to walk
you back to your cottage?

50:24.355 --> 50:26.356
No.
We're fine.

50:26.357 --> 50:27.624
You sure about that?

50:27.625 --> 50:30.460
You wouldn't want to walk
into the wrong place.

50:30.461 --> 50:31.628
Why?

50:31.629 --> 50:35.132
Is there something you
don't want us to see?

50:35.133 --> 50:39.870
It's just an expression, friend.

50:39.871 --> 50:43.974
It's late, you want to go poking
around other people's business,

50:43.975 --> 50:46.009
you go right on ahead.

50:46.010 --> 50:48.712
But if you put your hand
into the dog's bone,

50:48.713 --> 50:51.848
don't be surprised if you get bit.

50:51.849 --> 50:54.384
What's that supposed to mean?

50:54.385 --> 50:56.753
You boys have a nice evening.

50:56.754 --> 51:00.155
Sam, let's just drop it.

51:04.361 --> 51:06.362
Patrick?
Sam, come on.

51:11.034 --> 51:12.801
Shit.

51:15.739 --> 51:17.174
What the fuck is going on here?

51:17.175 --> 51:18.508
Did he just threaten us?

51:18.509 --> 51:20.277
I'm not sure.

51:20.278 --> 51:22.612
Do you think he knows
we were in the office?

51:22.613 --> 51:25.115
Anyway, is Patrick's
sister hiding his files?

51:25.116 --> 51:27.918
I know she is not supposed to be.

51:27.919 --> 51:29.920
They're just using Patrick?

51:29.921 --> 51:31.021
I don't know.

51:31.022 --> 51:33.455
I don't know what's
going on anymore.

51:37.260 --> 51:38.929
This is too fucked up.

51:38.930 --> 51:40.430
These people are happy living here.

51:40.431 --> 51:42.432
Good for them, but I don't
want to get any more involved.

51:42.433 --> 51:44.901
I'm done.

51:44.902 --> 51:47.437
Also, if she's getting high
and sleeping with the guy,

51:47.438 --> 51:48.905
what's the point of this place?

51:48.906 --> 51:52.309
It's supposed to be
sober living, right?

51:52.310 --> 51:54.711
I mean, she looks an awful lot
like the fucked up sister

51:54.712 --> 51:57.079
Patrick was describing.

52:23.240 --> 52:27.310
Savannah?
Where is she, dude?

52:27.311 --> 52:28.478
Where did she go?

52:28.479 --> 52:30.612
I don't know.

52:51.835 --> 52:54.604
Please, take us with you.

52:54.605 --> 52:55.872
What?

52:55.873 --> 52:57.507
You don't know what's
really going on here.

52:57.508 --> 52:59.643
They will kill us if they
know we were talking to you.

52:59.644 --> 53:00.777
Who?

53:00.778 --> 53:01.878
Father.

53:01.879 --> 53:03.880
This place is not
what it seems like.

53:03.881 --> 53:06.016
They hurt people who
go against the Parish.

53:06.017 --> 53:07.851
Please, you have to help us.

53:07.852 --> 53:09.286
Wait, wait, wait, wait.
What do you mean?

53:09.287 --> 53:11.655
They keep it secret,
but it happens.

53:11.656 --> 53:13.523
Father will not let us leave.
We're prisoners here.

53:13.524 --> 53:15.792
You are being manipulated.

53:15.793 --> 53:18.895
We talked with plenty other
people, they all seemed happy.

53:18.896 --> 53:20.030
No.

53:20.031 --> 53:22.899
You talked with who Father
wanted you to talk with.

53:22.900 --> 53:26.903
Many other people won't tell you
but they are afraid to speak out.

53:26.904 --> 53:29.539
You don't understand the hold
he has over a lot of them,

53:29.540 --> 53:32.409
they're brainwashed and don't even
know it, they'll do anything he asks.

53:32.410 --> 53:34.511
Your friend's sister
is one of them.

53:34.512 --> 53:36.913
She has done terrible things
to people who act tough.

53:36.914 --> 53:39.049
Savannah saw them.

53:39.050 --> 53:43.019
They beat my daughter, that's
why she won't speak anymore.

53:43.020 --> 53:45.422
Please, please, help us.

53:45.423 --> 53:47.390
I don't know what we can do.

53:47.391 --> 53:48.825
Our helicopter comes
in the morning,

53:48.826 --> 53:50.827
but it's not big enough to
carry many more people out.

53:50.828 --> 53:51.928
Then just take my daughter.

53:51.929 --> 53:52.929
What?

53:52.930 --> 53:55.065
Please, don't let her die.
I beg you.

53:55.066 --> 53:57.334
Shh! Ssh!
Somebody is coming.

53:57.335 --> 53:58.934
Oh, God.

54:00.537 --> 54:03.038
Hey, it's okay.
It's okay.

54:04.574 --> 54:06.209
What is going on here?

54:06.210 --> 54:07.544
We found her wandering out here.

54:07.545 --> 54:10.347
We're trying to find out where she lives.
She doesn't talk much.

54:10.348 --> 54:11.348
I will take her.

54:11.349 --> 54:12.349
Oh, it's okay.
We can do it.

54:12.350 --> 54:15.217
I know where she lives.
I will take her.

54:17.687 --> 54:20.557
Where is your mother, Savannah?

54:20.558 --> 54:23.693
I will go tell Father.

54:23.694 --> 54:25.227
Let's go.

54:32.369 --> 54:35.872
Jesus Christ.

54:35.873 --> 54:37.874
Come on.

54:37.875 --> 54:39.741
Let's just get back inside.

54:41.444 --> 54:44.314
They were terrified.

54:44.315 --> 54:46.983
We shouldn't have let him take her.
Why the fuck did we let them take her?

54:46.984 --> 54:49.085
What were we supposed to do?

54:49.086 --> 54:51.121
We can't take anyone with us.

54:51.122 --> 54:52.756
We could've done something.

54:52.757 --> 54:54.124
Sam, it's not why we're here.

54:54.125 --> 54:56.593
It's not our problem.

54:56.594 --> 55:00.230
It's not why we make these films,
you're losing sight of things.

55:00.231 --> 55:03.333
We can report this when we get back,
but it's not up to us to decide

55:03.334 --> 55:04.901
what happens to these people.

55:04.902 --> 55:07.270
We're not the Red Cross.

55:07.271 --> 55:08.838
Did you see those scars?

55:08.839 --> 55:12.108
How could she let her
daughter be beaten like that?

55:12.109 --> 55:13.643
<i>That's all for tonight.</i>

55:13.644 --> 55:16.146
